铯[[原子钟|原子钟]]观察铯-133原子在[[超精细结构|超精细结构]]之间跃迁产生的[[电磁辐射|电磁辐射]]，并以此作为参考点。1955年，第一个精确的铯原子钟由[[路易斯·艾森|路易斯·艾森]]在[[英国国家物理实验室|英国国家物理实验室]]建成<ref>{{Cite journal |first1=L.|last=Essen|first2=J.V.L.|last2=Parry |year=1955 |title=An Atomic Standard of Frequency and Time Interval: A Cesium Resonator |journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] |volume=176 |pages=280 |doi=10.1038/176280a0|bibcode = 1955Natur.176..280E |issue=4476}}</ref>。在过去的半个多世纪中，人们不停的改进铯原子钟，并且使用它作为标准时间和频率测量的基准。这些-{zh-hans:钟; zh-hant:鐘;}-测量频率的精度为2-3×10<sup>-14</sup>，相当于时间测量的精度为每天2纳秒，或者140万年1秒。目前最先进的铯原子钟的精度超过了10<sup>-15</sup>，这意味着从6600万年前[[白垩纪－第三纪灭绝事件|恐龙灭绝]]的时代起其误差仅为2秒钟<ref name="USGS" />，被认为是“人类目前所达到的最精确的单位实现”<ref name="USNO" />。

铯原子钟也用于监控手机时间传输以及互联网信息流的网络中<ref>{{cite news|first = Monte|last = Reel|date = 2003-07-22|title = Where timing truly is everything|newspaper = Washington Post|page = B1|url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-284155.html|accessdate = 2010-01-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130429044454/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-284155.html|archive-date = 2013-04-29|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

===电力电子===
铯蒸气[[热离子发电机|热离子发电机]]是将热能转化为电能的低功率装置。在双电机[[真空管|真空管]]转换器中，铯将在阴极聚集的空间电荷清除，并通过这种方式增强电流<ref>{{cite journal| last1 = Rasor| first1 = Ned S.| first2 = Charles|last2 =Warner| title = Correlation of Emission Processes for Adsorbed Alkali Films on Metal Surfaces| journal = Journal of Applied Physics| volume = 35| issue = 9| pages = 2589–2600| date = September 1964|doi = 10.1063/1.1713806|bibcode = 1964JAP....35.2589R}}</ref>。

铯也因其具有[[光电效应|光电发射]]的性质而重要，它可以将光能转化为电流。由于诸如金属化合物{{chem|K|2|CsSb}}等的铯基阴极发射电子的电压阈值较低，通常将铯用于[[光电池|光电池]]中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.americanelements.com/cs.html |title=Cesium Supplier & Technical Information |publisher=American Elements |accessdate=2010-01-25 |archive-date=2010-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100116183321/http://americanelements.com/cs.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。使用铯的光电发射装置包括[[光学字符识别|光学字符识别]]装置、[[光电倍增管|光电倍增管]]以及[[摄像管|摄像管]]<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1063/1.3215593|title = K <sub>2</sub>CsSb Cathode Development| journal = American Institute of Physics Conference Proceedings |year = 2009|volume = 1149| pages = 1062–1066|first1 =John|last1 = Smedley| first2 =Triveni|last2 = Rao| first3 =Erdong|last3 = Wang}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|first = P.|last = Görlich|title = Über zusammengesetzte, durchsichtige Photokathoden|journal = Zeitschrift für Physik|volume = 101|pages = 335–342|year =1936|doi =10.1007/BF01342330|bibcode = 1936ZPhy..101..335G|issue = 5–6}}</ref>。尽管如此，[[锗|锗]]、[[铷|铷]]、[[硒|硒]]、[[硅|硅]]、[[碲|碲]]以及其他几种元素可以替代铯作为光电发射材料<ref name="USGS" />。

[[碘化铯|碘化铯]]（CsI）、[[溴化铯|溴化铯]]（CsBr）以及[[氟化铯|氟化铯]]（CsF）晶体可以用于[[闪烁计数器|闪烁计数器]]中的[[闪烁体|闪烁体]]。由于闪烁计数器适用于检测[[伽玛射线|伽玛射线]]和[[X射线|X射线]]，它们广泛的用于矿物勘探以及粒子物理学研究中。由于铯的原子量较大，可以提供较好的停止能力，因此可以提高检测能力。铯化合物也提供了更快的响应速度（CsF）并且不易吸水（CsI）。

铯蒸气用于许多普通[[磁强计|磁强计]]中<ref>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1007/s00340-005-1773-x|title = Comparison of discharge lamp and laser pumped cesium magnetometers|year = 2005|last1 = Groeger|first1 = S.|first2 = A. S.|first3 = A.|journal = Applied Physics B|volume = 80|pages = 645–654|last2 = Pazgalev|last3 = Weis|arxiv = physics/0412011 |bibcode = 2005ApPhB..80..645G|issue = 6}}</ref>。铯也在[[分光光度法|分光光度法]]中作为[[内部标准|内部标准]]使用<ref>{{cite book|url = http://books.google.com/?id=z9SzvsSCHv4C&pg=PA108|page = 108|isbn = 978-0-471-28572-4|chapter = Internal Standards|year = 1994|first1=Mary C.|last1=Haven|first2=Gregory A.|last2=Tetrault|first3=Jerald R.|last3=Schenken|publisher = John Wiley and Sons|location = New York|title = Laboratory instrumentation}}</ref>。和其它碱金属类似，铯和[[氧|氧]]的联系紧密，因此在真空管中铯被用作[[吸气剂|吸气剂]]<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/?id=1o1WECNJkscC&pg=PA391&lpg=391 |title=Photo-electronic image devices: proceedings of the fourth symposium held at Imperial College, London, September 16–20, 1968|volume = 1|publisher = Academic Press|year = 1969|first = James D.|last = McGee|page = 391|isbn=978-0-12-014528-7}}</ref>。铯还用于[[激光|高能激光]]、[[日光灯|蒸气辉光灯]]以及蒸气[[整流器|整流器]]中<ref name="USGS" />。

===离心液===
由于其密度较高，氯化铯、硫化铯、以及[[三氟乙酸|三氟乙酸铯]]通常在分子生物学中用于密度梯度离心操作<ref>Manfred Bick, Horst Prinz, "Cesium and Cesium Compounds" in Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry 2005, Wiley-VCH, Weinheim. {{DOI|10.1002/14356007.a06 153}}.</ref>。该技术主要用于分离生物样本中的[[病毒|病毒颗粒]]、[[细胞器|细胞器]]以及[[核酸|核酸]]<ref>{{cite book|url = http://books.google.com/?id=1kn89nI2gUsC&pg=PA61|pages = 61–62|isbn = 978-0-89603-564-5|chapter = Gradient Materials|editor =Desai, Mohamed A.|year = 2000|publisher = Humana Press|location = Totowa, N.J.|title = Downstream processing methods}}</ref>。

===化学与医学应用===
[[File:Caesium_chloride.jpg|thumb]]
铯在化学上的应用相对较少<ref>{{cite book |last = Burt|first =R. O.|year = 1993|chapter= Cesium and cesium compounds|title = Kirk-Othmer encyclopedia of chemical technology|edition = 4th|place = New York|publisher = John Wiley & Sons|volume = 5|page =759|isbn = 978-0-471-15158-6}}</ref>。铯的化合物通常用于增强若干化学品生产中的金属-离子催化剂的作用，这些化学品包括[[丙烯酸|丙烯酸]]、[[环氧乙烷|环氧乙烷]]、[[蒽醌|蒽醌]]、[[甲醇|甲醇]]、[[邻苯二甲酸酐|邻苯二甲酸酐]]、[[苯乙烯|苯乙烯]]、[[甲基丙烯酸甲酯|甲基丙烯酸甲酯]][[单体|单体]]以及各种[[烯烃|烯烃]]等等。铯化合物也用于在硫酸生产中将二氧化硫催化转化为三氧化硫的过程中<ref name="USGS" />。
 <!--No way: Cesium metal is also used in ferrous and nonferrous [[metallurgy|metallurgy]] and in the purification of [[carbon_dioxide|carbon dioxide]] as it absorbs gases and other impurities, while molten hydroxide (CsOH) has been used in the desulfurizing of heavy crude oil.<ref name="USGS" /> -->

[[氟化铯|氟化铯]]在[[有机化学|有机化学]]中被用作碱<ref name="greenwood"/>或者[[氟|氟]]离子的来源<ref>
Friestad, Gregory K.; Branchaud, Bruce P.; Navarrini, Walter and Sansotera, Maurizio (2007) "Cesium Fluoride" in ''Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis'', John Wiley & Sons. {{DOI|10.1002/047084289X.rc050.pub2}}</ref>。铯盐在合成[[环状化合物|环状化合物]]、[[酯|酯]]以及[[聚合|聚合]]等[[有机合成|有机合成]]中有时用来替代钾盐或者钠盐。

===核应用与同位素应用===

[[铯-137|铯-137]]在工业应用中是一种非常常见的作为[[伽玛射线|伽玛射线]]发射源的同位素。其优势在于它的半衰期大约30年，可以通过[[核燃料循环|核燃料循环]]获得，并且其最终产物[[钡-137|钡-137]]是一种稳定的同位素。其较高的水溶性是其缺点，使得它无法用在用于食品和医疗用品的大型池式辐射器中<ref name="Takeshi">{{cite web|url = http://earth1.epa.gov/radiation/docs/source-management/csfinallongtakeshi.pdf|title = The material flow of radioactive cesium-137 in the U.S. 2000|first = Takeshi|last = Okumura|date = 2003-10-21|format = PDF|accessdate = 2009-12-20|publisher = United States Environmental Protection Agency|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110720163223/http://earth1.epa.gov/radiation/docs/source-management/csfinallongtakeshi.pdf|archivedate = 2011-07-20}}</ref>。铯-137已经被用在农业、癌症治疗、食品消毒、污水污泥处理以及外科手术设备中。<ref name="USGS" /><ref>{{cite book|last = Jensen|first = N. L.|year = 1985|chapter=Cesium|title = Mineral facts and problems|publisher = U.S. Bureau of Mines|volume = Bulletin 675|pages = 133–138}}</ref>。铯的放射性同位素可以用在[[放射线疗法|放射线疗法]]中针对某些癌症治疗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.medicalnewstoday.com/releases/91994.php|title=IsoRay's Cesium-131 Medical Isotope Used In Milestone Procedure Treating Eye Cancers At Tufts-New England Medical Center|date=2007-12-17|publisher=Medicalnewstoday.com|accessdate=2010-02-15|archive-date=2011-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110613221843/http://www.medicalnewstoday.com/releases/91994.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而由于目前已经有了更好的替代品，且放射源中易溶于水的[[氯化铯|氯化铯]]可能造成大范围污染，放疗中逐渐不再采用铯放射源<ref>{{Cite book|url = http://books.google.com/books?id=bk0go_-FO5QC&pg=PA22|isbn = 978-0-07-005115-7|chapter = Cesium-137 Machines|title = Radiation therapy planning|first = Gunilla Carleson|last = Bentel|publisher = McGraw-Hill Professional|year = 1996|accessdate = 2010-09-26|pages = 22–23|archive-date = 2013-06-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130602200152/http://books.google.com/books?id=bk0go_-FO5QC&pg=PA22|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|isbn = 978-0-309-11014-3|url = http://books.google.com/books?id=3cT2REdXJ98C|title = Radiation source use and replacement: abbreviated version|author = National Research Council (U.S.). Committee on Radiation Source Use and Replacement|publisher = National Academies Press|year = 2008|access-date = 2013-12-28|archive-date = 2014-01-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140107222907/http://books.google.com/books?id=3cT2REdXJ98C|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在许多工业测量计中都采用了铯-137，包括湿度计、密度计、水平仪以及厚度计<ref name="gauges">{{cite book|chapter = Level and density measurement using non-contact nuclear gauges|isbn = 978-0-412-53400-3|url =http://books.google.com/?id=RwsoQbHYjvwC&pg=PA82|pages = 82–85|editor= Loxton, R., Pope, P.|year = 1995|publisher = Chapman & Hall|location = London|title = Instrumentation : A Reader}}</ref>。[[测井|测井]]设备中也会使用铯-137来测量与岩层中的电子密度<ref>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1146/annurev.ea.13.050185.001531|title = Downhole Geophysical Logging|year = 1985|last1 = Timur|first1 = A.|last2 = Toksoz|first2 = M. N.|journal = Annual Review of Earth and Planetary Sciences|volume = 13|page = 315|bibcode = 1985AREPS..13..315T}}</ref>。

铯-137也用于[[水文学|水文学]]研究中。铯是核裂变反应的产物。自从大约1945年[[核试验|核试验]]开始，一直到20世纪80年代中期，铯137被释放进入大气层，然后立即被吸收入水溶液中。那个时期的年度变化与土壤和沉积层有相关性。铯-134以及含量更少的铯-135也用于水文学研究作为核电工业中产生的铯的度量。这两种同位素不像铯-133或者铯-137那样常见，而且仅能通过人为过程产生<ref>{{Cite journal|first=Carol|last=Kendall|url=http://wwwrcamnl.wr.usgs.gov/isoig/period/cs_iig.html|title=Isotope Tracers Project – Resources on Isotopes – Cesium|publisher=National Research Program – U.S. Geological Survey|accessdate=2010-01-25|journal=|archive-date=2010-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100529185157/http://wwwrcamnl.wr.usgs.gov/isoig/period/cs_iig.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。<!--http://books.google.com/books?id=pWDQnxd-r1UC&pg=PT360 &pg=PT12 -->

===其它应用===
[[File:Electrostatic_ion_thruster-en.svg|thumb]]

在早期的为长距离星际航行的[[航天器推进|航天器推进]]器设计的[[离子推力器|离子推力器]]中使用铯和汞作为推进剂。在离子化方法中，需要通过与加载电压的[[钨|钨]]电极接触剥去推进剂的外层电子。考虑到铯对飞船部件的腐蚀作用，对离子推进器的研发转向使用惰性气体推进剂，例如[[氙|氙]]。在地面测试中处理惰性气体推进剂，并且其对飞船造成影响的可能性也更小<ref name="USGS" />。最终在1998年发射的试验飞船[[深空1号|深空1号]]中使用氙作为推进剂<ref>{{cite journal|doi =10.1063/1.1150468|title =NSTAR Xenon Ion Thruster on Deep Space 1: Ground and flight tests (invited)|year =2000|last1 =Marcucci|first1 =M. G.|last2 =Polk|first2 =J. E.|journal =Review of Scientific Instruments|volume =71|pages =1389–1400|bibcode = 2000RScI...71.1389M|issue =3}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = http://gltrs.grc.nasa.gov/reports/1999/TM-1999-209439.pdf|format = PDF|title = A Synopsis of Ion Propulsion Development Projects in the United States: SERT I to Deep Space I|first1 = James S.|last1 = Sovey|first2 = Vincent K.|last2 = Rawlin|first3 = Michael J|last3 = Patterson|publisher = NASA|accessdate = 2009-12-12|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090629225625/http://gltrs.grc.nasa.gov/reports/1999/TM-1999-209439.pdf|archivedate = 2009-06-29}}</ref>。尽管如此，已经建造的[[场发射电子推进|场发射电子推进]]推力器仍然使用加速诸如铯等的金属离子的简单系统来形成推力。<ref>{{cite conference|url=http://trs-new.jpl.nasa.gov/dspace/handle/2014/11649|title=In-FEEP Thruster Ion Beam Neutralization with Thermionic and Field Emission Cathodes|format=PDF|conference=27th International Electric Propulsion Conference|place=Pasadena, California|pages=1–15|accessdate=2010-09-26|author=Marrese, C.; Polk, J.; Mueller, J.; Owens, A.; Tajmar, M.; Fink, R. and Spindt, C.|date=October 2001|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527071653/http://trs-new.jpl.nasa.gov/dspace/handle/2014/11649|archivedate=2010-05-27}}</ref>

在[[红外|红外]][[照明弹|照明弹]]中使用[[硝酸铯|硝酸铯]]作为[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]和[[烟火着色剂|烟火着色剂]]来燃烧[[硅|硅]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.freepatentsonline.com/6230628.html |work=United States Patent 6230628 |title=Infrared illumination compositions and articles containing the same |publisher=Freepatentsonline.com |accessdate=2010-01-25 |archive-date=2011-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110614045347/http://www.freepatentsonline.com/6230628.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，例如LUU-19照明弹<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.fas.org/man/dod-101/sys/dumb/luu19.htm|title = LUU-19 Flare|publisher = Federation of American Scientists|date = 2000-04-23|accessdate = 2009-12-12|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110609030345/http://www.fas.org/man/dod-101/sys/dumb/luu19.htm|archivedate = 2011-06-09}}</ref>。这是因为硝酸铯的大部分辐射光都位于[[近红外光谱|近红外光谱]]中<ref>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1016/j.tca.2006.04.002|title = Determination of the temperature and enthalpy of the solid–solid phase transition of cesium nitrate by differential scanning calorimetry|year = 2006|last1 = Charrier|first1 = E.|first2 = E.L.|first3 = P.G.|first4 = H.M.|first5 = B.|first6 = T.T.|journal = Thermochimica Acta|volume = 445|pages = 36–39 |last2 = Charsley|last3 = Laye|last4 = Markham|last5 = Berger|last6 = Griffiths}}</ref>。铯也被用来减少[[SR-71黑鸟式侦察机|SR-71黑鸟式侦察机]]的[[尾气|尾焰]]的[[雷达散射截面|雷达特征]]<ref>{{cite book|isbn = 978-1-84176-098-8|page = [https://archive.org/details/lockheedsr71secr0000cric/page/47 47]|title=Lockheed SR-71: the secret missions exposed|url = https://archive.org/details/lockheedsr71secr0000cric|last=Crickmore|first = Paul F.|publisher=Osprey|year=2000}}</ref>。铯也经常和铷一起以碳酸盐的形式加入玻璃以减少玻璃的导电性并且增加[[光纤|光纤]]与[[夜视镜|夜视设备]]的稳定性和持久性。氟化铯或者氟化铝铯也用在以含[[镁|镁]][[铝|铝]]合金钎焊的焊剂配方中<ref name="USGS" />。

==健康以及安全危害==

[[File:AirDoseChernobylVector.svg|thumb]]

大多数人极少能碰到铯的化合物，但是由于铯的化学性质接近钾，大多数化合物只有轻微的毒性。暴露在大量的铯化合物中会引起[[应激性|应急过度]]以及[[痉挛|痉挛]]，但是由于在自然情况下不会遇到这样大的剂量，铯并不是重要的化学环境污染物<ref>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1080/10934528109375003|title = Cesium in mammals: Acute toxicity, organ changes and tissue accumulation|year = 1981|last1 = Pinsky|first1 = Carl|first2 = Ranjan|first3 = J. R.|first4 = Jasper|first5 = Claude|first6 = James|journal = Journal of Environmental Science and Health, Part A|volume = 16|pages = 549– 567 |last2 = Bose|last3 = Taylor|last4 = McKee|last5 = Lapointe|last6 = Birchall|issue = 5}}</ref>。在小鼠试验中，氯化铯的[[半致死量|半致死量]]（LD<sub>50</sub>）为每千克体重2.3克，与[[氯化钾|氯化钾]]和[[氯化钠|氯化钠]]的半致死量相近<ref>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1016/0041-008X(75)90216-1|title = Acute toxicity of cesium and rubidium compounds|year = 1975|last1 = Johnson|first1 = Garland T.|journal = [[Toxicology_and_Applied_Pharmacology|Toxicology and Applied Pharmacology]]|volume = 32|pages = 239–245|pmid = 1154391|first2 = Trent R.|first3 = D. Wagner|issue = 2|last2 = Lewis|last3 = Wagner}}</ref>。

